<bibRefCitation id="A63A7FB21C2CFFF0FE2AF89ED94EF1EC" author="Gavrilov-Zimin I. A." box="[474,796,1919,1946]" pageId="1" pageNumber="51" pagination="1 - 260" refId="ref4551" refString="Gavrilov-Zimin I. A. 2018. Ontogenesis, morphology and higher classification of archaecococcids (Homoptera: Coccinea: Orthezioidea). Zoosystematica Rossica Supplementum 2: 1 - 260. https: // doi. org / 10.31610 / zsr / 2018. supl. 2.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Gavrilov-Zimin, 2018: 159</bibRefCitation>
